 <html><head><title> Visiting teacher network</title><!!keys: ></head><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#000066" vlink="#FF6600"><a href="../info/index.html"><img src="../pix/logo-t.gif" width=96 height=41 hspace=10vspace=2 border=0 align=right></a><h6 align=left>The material that follows has been provided by <ahref="../info/index.html">ACTIONAID</a></h6><br clear=right><br><h2 align=center> Visiting teacher network</h2><p>Our network of teachers provides a professional service to support classroom work. Teachers can offerslide presentations or activity-based sessions on a variety of localities or issues relevant to ACTIONAID'swork and the study of development issues in the classroom.<p>Our teachers are happy to adapt and devise sessions to meet your particular needs. Schools that havealready taken advantage of this service describe the sessions as "educational and stimulating" and "bringinga locality to life".<p>There is an all-inclusive charge of £45 for this service. If you would like more details or to book a visit,please tick the box on the <b><a href="order.html">order form</a></b>. <p><hr><p><a href="../home.html"><img src="../pix/home.gif" width=46 height=41 hspace=10vspace=2 border=0 align=right></a><a href="../fight/index.html" target="_parent"><img src="../pix/globe1.gif" width=46 height=41hspace=10 vspace=2 border=0 align=right></a> <a href="resource.html"><img src="../pix/back.gif" width=46height=41hspace=10 vspace=2 border=0 align=right></a><font size=1 face=helvetica, arial><b><li type=square><a href="../home.html">Home Page</a> <li type=square><ahref="../fight/index.html" target="_parent">JoinACTIONAID</a> <li type=square><a href="resource.html">Resources for teachers</a></b></font><br clear=all><p></body></html>
