<HTML>
<HEAD>
<title>The "New Europe" and the Caribbean</title>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<center><img src="../images/cedla.gif"></center><br clear><br>  
<H2><center>
The 'New Europe' and the Caribbean<br>
</h2><H4>by <i>Paul Sutton</i></H4>
<h4>Full text of an article published in <i>European Review of Latin American and Caribbean Studies,</i><br>number 59, December 1995: pp. 37 - 57.
<p></h4>
</center>
<hr>
<P>
<h3>Contents:</h3>
