<title>Development Cooperation and the Lom&#233; Convention</title>
</header>
<hr>
<h3><center><IMG SRC ="images/acp.jpg"> <IMG SRC  = "images/eu.jpg"><p>
Background Texts on the Future of the Lom&#233; Convention<br>Documents de r&#233;f&#233;rence portant sur l'avenir des relations UE-ACP au-del&#224; de Lom&#233; IV</h3>
</center>
<p>
<hr>
