<h2><i>Instruments of Technical Cooperation</a></i></h2>
<ul type=square>
<li><A HREF = "iaac/abp.htm">Area-based programmes in the Irish bilateral aid programme: Thinking towards best practice</a>. (<i>IAAC Informal Paper, 1996</i>) <img src="images/new.gif">
