<p>
<li><a href="dpmn/943st_gb.htm">Partnership in agricultural research</a>.  (<i>DPMN Bulletin, December 1994</i>) 
<p>
<li><a href="../ecdpm/pmb/b3s_gb.htm">Partnership in the 1990's</a>: How to make it work better. (<i>ECDPM Policy Management Brief, 1994</i>)
<p>
<li><a href="dpmn/943hg_gb.htm">A perspective from an international NGO</a>.  (<i>DPMN Bulletin, December 1994</i>)
<p>
