<p>
<li><a href="dpmn/943ff_gb.htm">Weaknesses and arrogance in development cooperation</a>. (<i>DPMN Bulletin, December 1994</i>) 
<p>
</ul>
<hr><h2><i>Stakeholder Analysis</i></h2>
<ul type=square>
<li><A HREF="http:../../oda/publications/stake1.html">How To Do Stakeholder Analysis Of Aid Projects And Programmes</a>. (<i>ODA Technical Note, July 1995</i>)
<p>
<li><A HREF="http:../../oda/publications/stake2.html">Enhancing Stakeholder Participation In Aid Activities</a>. (<i>ODA Technical Note, July 1995</i>)
<p>
<li><A HREF="http:../../oda/publications/stake3.html">Indicators For Measuring And Assessing Primary Stakeholder Participation</a>. (<i>ODA Technical Note, July 1995</i>)
</ul>

</ul>
</ul>
<hr>
<p>
<IMG ALIGN=left SRC="images/home.jpg"><br><A HREF = "euf_gb.htm#top">Go To EUFORIC Home Page</a> / <A HREF = "indx.htm">index</a>

</h5>
