<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000576-B047-186</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/dandc/94e_bra.htm 193.128.6.150 19970213145752 text/html 13892
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 14:57:04 GMT
