<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000560-B042-108</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/ni/268_razor.html 193.128.6.150 19970213102441 text/html 10783
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 10:24:20 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Tue, 22 Aug 1995 16:02:12 GMT
