<P><BR></P>

<H1>The Organisation</H1>

<P>

Interaid is a non profit making company based in the UK. It is working to link

up schools in the Commonwealth via the Internet. This will provide children

throughout the world with the opportunity to communicate and learn from each

other through a

<A HREF="global.htm">Global School </A>network.  </P> 

<CENTER><P> 

<A HREF="global.htm"><STRONG>Global School </STRONG></A></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P> 

<A HREF="short1.htm"><STRONG>April 1996 Newsletter </STRONG></A></P><P> 

<A HREF="short2.htm"><STRONG>May 1996  Newsletter</STRONG></A></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P>

<A HREF="newslett.htm"><STRONG>Subscribe to Electronic Newsletter</STRONG></A>

 

<BR></P></CENTER>

<P>This site will be regularly updated - add it to your list of favourite sites

now so that you can revisit us easily. Alternatively, subscribe to our

<A HREF="newslett.htm">electronic newsletter</A> and receive regular updates by

E-mail.

</P> 

<HR>

<P><A HREF="#top">Top</A></P>

