<DOCNO>WT17-B14-195</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000560-B042-298</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/odi/apartheid.html 193.128.6.150 19970213102629 text/html 3845
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 10:26:06 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Wed, 30 Oct 1996 16:11:37 GMT
