<title>Development Cooperation and Policy in Austria</title>
</header>
<hr>
<H3><center><IMG SRC  = "images/at.jpg">
<h3>Entwicklungspolitik von &#214;sterreich<br>Development Policy and Cooperation in Austria<br>Coop&#233;ration au d&#233;veloppement de l'Autriche</h3>
</center>
<p><hr>
<I>Reports / Rapports</I>
<ul><h5>
<li><a href="at/dcrat_gb.htm">DAC aid review of Austria</a> (<i>DAC Press Release, 1996</i>) <img src="images/new.gif">
<P>
<li><a href="vidc/rep1-96.htm">Entwicklungsl&auml;nder: Keine Partner f&uuml;r &Ouml;sterreichs Forschung?</a> (<i>VIDC Report Series 1/96, 1996) <img src="images/new.gif">
<p>
<li><a href="at/advis_at.htm">NAR Report on Development Cooperation Advisory Structures</a> (1994)
<p>

</ul>

