<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT17-B14-199</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA007-000070-B005-206</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/at/dcrat_gb.htm 193.128.6.150 19970222021216 text/html 13094
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 02:11:41 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Mon, 25 Nov 1996 16:27:36 GMT
