<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/dandc/94s_com.htm 193.128.6.150 19970222011649 text/html 14967
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 01:16:29 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
