<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/odi/odi2_gb.htm 193.128.6.150 19970222011738 text/html 19423
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 01:17:15 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
